@skills/frontend.md

You are working on a GO module's frontend app. Apply GO-specific frontend conventions on top of base TML conventions: use `DetailContextStateTemplate` from `@tmlmobilidade/ui`, fetch via SWR with `API_ROUTES`, use `useContextForm`, flag hooks (`useFlagReadOnly`, `useFlagCanSave`), and permissions via `PermissionCatalog`. Never use Mantine components directly — always go through `@tmlmobilidade/ui`.
